org.bff.javampd

Class MPD

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bff.javampd.MPD
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Server

    public class MPD
extends Object
implements Server
    MPD represents a connection to a MPD server. The commands are maintained in a properties file called mpd.properties.

    Uses the builder pattern for construction. Use MPD.Builder.build() to construct.

    Defaults are: server --> localhost port --> 6600 no timeout no password

    Author:
    Bill
